@startuml
[*] --> Start
Start --> WaitingForAmountSelection
WaitingForAmountSelection --> VerifyingTransaction: select predefined amount
WaitingForAmountSelection --> VerifyingTransaction: enter custom amount
VerifyingTransaction --> TransactionApproved: transaction approved
VerifyingTransaction --> TransactionRejected: transaction rejected
TransactionRejected --> WaitingForAmountSelection
@enduml
